description:
5G Towers are being put up while we’re all focusing on the Corona virus. The long term radiation effects of 5G have not been tested. Check your area to see if one is in your area. If they have put one up recently you must boycott it. Start at a petition and go to your local council. RAISE AWARENESS. Most people aren’t even aware these things are going up. Destroying nature, wildlife, trees and the cells in ours and our children’s body’s. Please check your area. We are in our rights to stop this 🛑 ✋ .
